data.description: Vintage Hills Community:This home offers excellent lighting,vaulted ceilings,large private yard,stainless appliances,granite counters,subway tile backsplash,washer/dryer(private laundry room),upgraded plank flooring,vaulted ceilings & large private view deck off master bedroom.Half-Bath downstairs!Pool/Spa/Park/BBQ Area/Basketball/Tennis/Playground within walking distance.Shopping,restaurants,award winning schools & Legends golf course within walking distance.Winery row is a short drive away.Go SOUTH on Meadows PRKWY from Rancho California Rd and you will see the BIG VINTAGE HILLS common area on your right...can't miss it...about a mile down Meadows Prkwy. There is also a park/pool/spa right down the street from the actual listing...about 100 yards away from front driveway:)
